sentences.en: He's working maybe twenty-five hours a week.
sentences.cn: 他一星期大约工作二十五个小时。

sentences.en: Twenty-five thousand turned out to be an overestimate.
sentences.cn: 25000这个数字被证实是过高的估计。

sentences.en: Twenty-five years ago they filled a time capsule and buried it.
sentences.cn: 25年前，他们装满一个时光宝盒并把它埋了起来。
